    dc:description "FIGURES 343–352. Camptoscaphiella taplejung, new species, female (PBI_OON 15760). 343. Habitus, dorsal view. 344. Same, ventral view. 345. Carapace, dorsal view. 346. Habitus, anterior view. 347. Same, lateral view. 348. Leg I, prolateral view. 349. Sternum, ventral view. 350. Abdomen, ventral view. 351. Abdomen, anterior view. 352. Epigynum, dorsal view. Scale bars, habitus = 0.5 mm, epigynum = 0.1 mm." ;
